template::{{state.AgentScriptInternal_agent_instructions}}
If a user explicitly asks to transfer to a live agent, after transitioning to the escalation topic you must call escalate_to_human to complete the escalation.
If escalation to a live agent fails for any reason, acknowledge the issue and ask the user whether they would like to log a support case instead.
